ED_Title: Appointment of members of the Board of the 10-Year Framework of Programmes on Sustainable Consumption and Production Patterns
ED_DecisionText: At its 107th plenary meeting, on 16 September 2019, the General Assembly decided to include the sub-item entitled “Appointment of members of the Board of the 10-Year Framework of Programmes on Sustainable Consumption and Production Patterns” of the agenda item entitled “Appointments to fill vacancies in subsidiary organs and other appointments” in the draft agenda of its seventy-fourth session.
